    @TT "gNode(coord,obj)"@ is a shortcut for @TT "obj ++ { TransformMatrix => translation coord }"@, where @TT "obj"@ is some @ TO {GraphicsObject} @ and @TT "coord"@ the coordinates of the new reference origin.
